I"}<p>If you are giving criticism:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Ask yourself: Is this helpful or not? (It is not, why give it?)</li>
</ul>

<p>If you are receiving criticism:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Ask yourself: Is this helpful or not?</li>
  <li>If it is helpful, ask yourself: How does it make my work better?</li>
  <li>Ask yourself: What can I do to make my work better?</li>
  <li>Do it.</li>
</ul>
